    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Grassy, public open spaces near the center of a town and used for a variety of community functions, found especially in New England and Mid-Atlantic states.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
